17:05.535 --> 17:07.770
Oh, what the hell is going on?

17:07.771 --> 17:09.538
Come on in, fellas.

17:12.008 --> 17:14.009
Nickels?

17:14.010 --> 17:16.377
You're out the hospital already?
I thought you were sick.

17:16.378 --> 17:19.314
We took care of that.

17:24.220 --> 17:25.988
I'm-a have a stent put
in my heart tomorrow.

17:25.989 --> 17:27.656
And because nothing is guaranteed,

17:27.656 --> 17:30.059
I figured I'd give you a chance
to apologize,

17:30.060 --> 17:32.661
