17:46.342 --> 17:49.378
I'm-I'm sorry.

17:49.379 --> 17:51.847
It was okay. It was only our career.

17:53.650 --> 17:55.184
And I can understand
why you might have thought

17:55.185 --> 17:56.819
I was flirting with your girl

17:56.820 --> 17:58.420
